# Re-enable JSON config files for the umbrella workspace (the **.json above
# was overly broad — meant to keep framework benchmark outputs out, but
# also caught package.json, tsconfig.json, tauri.conf.json, etc.)
!**/package.json
!**/tsconfig.json
!**/tsconfig.*.json
!**/tauri.conf.json
!**/vitest.config.json
!**/.vscode/*.json


